Description_lang: Fatescribe Roh-Kalo binds several players to runes upon the Loom of Fates.After $d, if a bound player is touching their assigned rune, the Fatescribe inflicts $354371s1 Shadow damage to all players within the rune.If a rune expires without its bound player inside, the Fatescribe inflicts $354372s1 Shadow damage to all players.
AuraDescription_lang: A nearby rune will explode for $354371s1 Shadow damage if you are not within its confines on expiration.
